

Q.1 What is your understanding of Block chain?
Ans: Block chain is the mixture of distributed database & cryptography technology. It is ledger having transaction records which ensures security, transparency & decentralization. Block chain is chain of blocks and each block has its own number

Q. 2 What is the core problem block chain trying to solve?
Ans: There are 3 core problems that block chain trying to solve
a)Authenticity
b) Security
c) Need of third party trust

Q.3. What are the few features which block chain will give u ..?
Ans: It consists of the following features:
a)Verifiable
b) Unchanged
c) Tamper-Proof
d ) Immutable

Q. 4 What all things does a Block Contain?
Ans: A block contain:-
a)Current Block Hash
b) Data Record of current block
c) Previous Block Hash
d) Signature
e)Mining Key

Q. 5How is the verifiability of Block chain is been attained ?
Ans: It can be attained by
Block 1 : 0 + new data = fingerprint1
Block 2 : fingerprint1+ new data =fingerprint2 ...chain continues.
